irmed by Cook's. We shall stop for a couple of days in New York so as to arrive in Hollywood on March 1st. It would be very kind if you could reserve for us living quarters at the Beverly Hills hotel. If you think that we shall be able to find a house or flat within a day or two, one large room with two beds would suffice; if this takes more time, we would like to have a bungalow, though smaller than the very large one we had last time, but still having bedroom and livingroom.

